data.title: Daewon Song and Almost Craziest Trick Giveaway!
data.description:
Almost Craziest Trick Instagram contest, featured in the Almost Famous show on Ride Channel!

Post your trick on Instagram with #AlmostCraziestTrick hash tag for a chance to win a a true one of a kind Daewon Song Batman board graphic on the size you ride.

We will feature entries on the next Almost Famous show EP #9, Tuesday April 22nd.
Winner will be chosen and announced on the following episode #10, Tuesday May 6th. 

Good Luck everyone, can't wait to see what everyone will be submitting.
